    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive 996.2 featuring the iconic wide-body silhouette and Turbo-spec suspension geometry. This example is powered by a 3.6L flat-six mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, with a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and rear-main seal replacement. Performance is anchored by a viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system and four-piston monoblock Brembo calipers over cross-drilled rotors. Meticulously maintained with zero bore scoring and a flawless factory finish, this C4S delivers a visceral, analog driving experience with unparalleled mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 49500.0,
